1
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:14,660
I really like you.

2
00:00:15,340 --> 00:00:16,379
Like me?

3
00:00:16,980 --> 00:00:18,219
Don't you just want to marry into the Gu family

4
00:00:18,219 --> 00:00:19,300
and marry into a rich family?

5
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:22,059
I did want to marry you before,

6
00:00:23,259 --> 00:00:24,579
but I've thought it through.

7
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:25,939
How could I possibly marry someone

8
00:00:25,939 --> 00:00:27,539
who secretly drugged me?

9
00:00:29,099 --> 00:00:31,099
You treated me like this when I was well.

10
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:32,419
Now that I'm blind,

11
00:00:32,620 --> 00:00:33,900
isn't it even more convenient for you?

12
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:36,300
I know you're under a lot of pressure.

13
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:38,020
I don't want to hear anything from you right now.

14
00:00:39,819 --> 00:00:40,739
I'm blind now.

15
00:00:40,739 --> 00:00:42,099
I can't see anything.

16
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,779
I could choose not to marry you,

17
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,779
but I can't leave you.

18
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:46,779
You need me.

19
00:00:46,779 --> 00:00:49,059
You accessed the company's core data without permission last night.

20
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:50,540
This is a serious violation.

21
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:52,260
You're fired.

22
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:53,779
Get out!

23
00:00:55,379 --> 00:00:56,700
The password is 35327.

24
00:00:57,580 --> 00:00:59,580
You can't help me

25
00:01:00,459 --> 00:01:01,859
without the core data.

26
00:01:13,659 --> 00:01:14,820
If you need me,

27
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:16,820
I'll come back.

28
00:02:01,219 --> 00:02:01,980
Xiaoxue,

29
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,460
I'm sorry to hurt you.

30
00:02:05,019 --> 00:02:06,179
I'm blind now.

31
00:02:07,019 --> 00:02:08,980
[Qi Zhu and her mother, who covet the position of chairman,]

32
00:02:09,139 --> 00:02:10,540
[are getting more and more aggressive.]

33
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:13,380
[I can't protect myself now,]

34
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,660
[let alone protect you.]

35
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:16,500
[Maybe]

36
00:02:17,019 --> 00:02:18,940
[it's best to let you go.]

37
00:02:20,299 --> 00:02:21,019
[I'm sorry.]

38
00:02:38,579 --> 00:02:40,579
Gu Chengyan really kicked Ji Xiaoxue out.

39
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,419
What?

40
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,419
You can't bear to part with her?

41
00:02:48,019 --> 00:02:48,859
No.

42
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:51,540
I just think if Ji Xiaoxue leaves,

43
00:02:52,139 --> 00:02:53,899
our plan will be...

44
00:02:56,339 --> 00:02:57,780
Men who are in love

45
00:02:58,299 --> 00:02:59,820
are like children.

46
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:02,060
The more you don't let him do something,

47
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,780
the more he wants to do it.

48
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:06,179
It's the same when you fall in love with a woman.

49
00:03:07,859 --> 00:03:10,179
But we can't let Ji Xiaoxue go.

50
00:03:10,899 --> 00:03:11,820
If she leaves,

51
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:14,859
our plan won't work.

52
00:03:36,419 --> 00:03:37,579
From now on, without my permission,

53
00:03:37,579 --> 00:03:38,859
you're not allowed to touch my stuff.

54
00:03:41,139 --> 00:03:42,380
I'm not sick, why am I taking medicine?

55
00:03:57,859 --> 00:03:59,500
Look at you in front of him,

56
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:02,459
you're just a dog wagging its tail.

57
00:04:07,179 --> 00:04:07,980
Young Master Yan,

58
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:09,619
don't you refuse to go to the rehabilitation room?

59
00:04:09,619 --> 00:04:11,660
Then I'll help you move all the fitness equipment here.

60
00:05:05,019 --> 00:05:05,700
Come in.

61
00:05:18,539 --> 00:05:19,339
Xiaoxue.

62
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:20,740
Is that you, Xiaoxue?

63
00:05:23,539 --> 00:05:24,420
No, Mr. Gu.

64
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:25,940
I'm here to clean up the trash.

65
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:31,740
Xiaoxue.

66
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:33,300
Mr. Gu, the meeting is about to start.

67
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:35,779
You go ahead.

68
00:05:35,779 --> 00:05:36,420
Okay.

69
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:49,700
Tell me.

70
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:51,740
What do you want to talk to me?

71
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,620
Although we are not biological brothers,

72
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:56,339
we have lived together for so many years.

73
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:58,060
I've long regarded you as my brother.

74
00:05:59,339 --> 00:06:01,339
We're both competing for the position of heir to the Gu family,

75
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,659
but it's all for the good of the Gu family.

76
00:06:03,659 --> 00:06:04,979
I have no intention of competing with you.

77
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:09,060
I used to always stand up for Wanqing

78
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:10,740
because

79
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:13,339
I didn't know you liked Ji Xiaoxue,

80
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:15,539
and Ji Xiaoxue likes you too.

81
00:06:19,219 --> 00:06:20,180
During this time,

82
00:06:21,019 --> 00:06:21,940
you thought she was gone,

83
00:06:23,579 --> 00:06:25,019
but she has always been by your side.

84
00:06:27,019 --> 00:06:27,779
Where is she?

85
00:06:31,339 --> 00:06:32,579
I won't bother you two.

86
00:06:33,779 --> 00:06:34,860
You can talk.

87
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:14,420
Xiaoxue,

88
00:07:17,219 --> 00:07:19,139
you... you can see again.

89
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,459
I can see you again.

90
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,139
I'm sorry.

91
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:31,940
I know you drove me away on purpose.

92
00:07:33,099 --> 00:07:33,860
I'm sorry.

93
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,860
No matter what happens in the future,

94
00:07:37,820 --> 00:07:39,659
don't drive me away, okay?

95
00:07:40,979 --> 00:07:41,659
Okay.

96
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:55,380
I knew they'd get together.

97
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,860
He's just pretending to break up with Ji Xiaoxue

98
00:07:59,099 --> 00:08:00,820
to get your shares.

99
00:08:02,539 --> 00:08:04,339
I did it to stop you from bullying her,

100
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:05,420
so I...

101
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:07,659
You can see again?

102
00:08:08,579 --> 00:08:10,539
You're a genius at acting.

103
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,700
One moment you're blind,

104
00:08:13,019 --> 00:08:14,139
the next you're limping.

105
00:08:15,139 --> 00:08:16,899
I should give you a round of applause.

106
00:08:17,339 --> 00:08:18,300
Whatever you think.

107
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:20,459
She's my girlfriend now.

108
00:08:22,019 --> 00:08:23,459
You can't bully her anymore.

109
00:08:24,219 --> 00:08:25,940
You put on such a big show,

110
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:27,740
I'll give you a good show too.

111
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:30,619
Actually, you and Ji Xiaoxue

112
00:08:31,099 --> 00:08:32,060
are siblings.

113
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:33,900
What nonsense are you talking about?

114
00:08:33,979 --> 00:08:35,579
My parents died long ago.

115
00:08:35,579 --> 00:08:37,219
I grew up in an orphanage.

116
00:08:37,219 --> 00:08:38,820
How could I possibly be his sister?

117
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:40,339
If you keep saying this

118
00:08:40,619 --> 00:08:42,499
to ruin Xiaoxue and the Gu Family's reputation,

119
00:08:42,859 --> 00:08:44,259
I won't let you get away with it.

120
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,339
She's not talking nonsense.

121
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:51,940
Xiaoxue,

122
00:08:52,579 --> 00:08:53,780
you are my daughter.
